📱 Privacy Policy for Maharan Vendor (Vendor App)

Maharan Vendor(“we,” “our,” or “us”) values your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you 
provide when using the Maharan Vendor mobile application (“App”). By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Maharan Vendor is designed to allow customers to collect, manage, and organize digital stamps from participating vendors. To provide these services, we may collect personal information such as 
your name, email address, phone number. We also collect location information, with your permission, to help you discover nearby vendors and access location-based rewards or offers. You can
choose to disable location permissions at any time in your device settings, though certain features may not function properly without it.

In addition, we may collect non-personal data such as device type, operating system, and usage analytics to help us improve app performance and the user experience. Notifications are used 
to alert you about rewards, offers, and important updates. You can manage your notification preferences within your device settings.

Your personal information is used solely to deliver and improve the services offered by Maharan Vendor, such as managing your stamp collections, connecting you with vendors, and personalizing your
in-app experience. We do not sell or rent your personal data to any third parties. Information may be shared only with trusted partners or service providers (e.g., cloud hosting, 
authentication, or analytics services) who assist us in operating the app, and all such parties are required to maintain the confidentiality and security of your data.

We use standard administrative, technical, and physical security measures to protect your information against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, no method of transmission over
the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

You have full control over your data. You may review, update, or delete your personal information or account at any time. If you wish to exercise your rights or have any questions about 
this policy, please contact us at ant.technepal@gmail.com
. We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time, and the latest version will always be available within the app or on our official website.

